sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as 👤 Cliente
    participant API as ⚙️ Backend API
    participant A as 🎨 Artista

    C->>API: POST /api/quotes/appointments/<br/>{artist_id, quote_id, scheduled_at}
    API-->>C: 201 · Appointment {status: PENDING}

    Note over A,API: Artista recibe nueva cita en su panel

    A->>API: PATCH /api/quotes/appointments/{id}/status/<br/>{status: COUNTER_OFFER,<br/>counter_offer_datetime,<br/>counter_offer_note}

    API->>API: Valida: status=PENDING ✔<br/>Actor = STUDIO dueño de cita ✔<br/>counter_offer_datetime requerida ✔

    API-->>A: 200 · Appointment {status: COUNTER_OFFER}

    Note over C,API: Cliente ve la contraoferta en "Mis Citas"

    alt ✅ Cliente acepta la contraoferta
        C->>API: PATCH /api/quotes/appointments/{id}/status/<br/>{status: APPROVED}
        API->>API: Valida: status=COUNTER_OFFER ✔<br/>Actor = CLIENT dueño ✔<br/>nuevo status = APPROVED ✔
        API-->>C: 200 · Appointment {status: APPROVED}
        Note over C: Cita confirmada → puede enviar HealthConsent
    else ❌ Estado inválido (REJECTED desde COUNTER_OFFER)
        C->>API: PATCH /api/quotes/appointments/{id}/status/<br/>{status: REJECTED}
        API-->>C: 400 · "Desde COUNTER_OFFER solo puede pasar a APPROVED."
    end
